=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_Env_ex21 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark mixed sound, with complex oscillator character around 50 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and impulsive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, energy distribution is front_heavy, and filtered with steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: impulsive
  envelope_flatness: very_dynamic
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: front_heavy

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 50.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: -0.0092
  harmonic_regularity: 0.1699
  pitch_clarity: 0.0406
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -6.6074
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Env Example 21
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/Env.html
// Tags: Env, Classes, envelope
// ---
// --- Example 21 ---
{ Blip.ar(50, 200, Env.perc(1, 0.1, 0.2).kr(2)) }.play;
(
{
    Blip.ar(
        Env({ exprand(3, 2000.0) } ! 18, 0.2, \exp).kr,
        200,
        Env({ rrand(0.1, 0.2) } ! 18 ++ 0, 0.2).kr(2))
    }.play;
)
